[Scene01]

Galdov was alive. Despite the evidence that was very clear before him, Bob found the truth hard to
accept. In his previous encounter with the evil leader of the BioMech invaders, Bob
had fought him for the Reality Crystal and left him to be destroyed along with the
alien space station.

[Scene02]

How had he survived? What strange and unimaginable powers did Galdov still possess
that Bob was unaware of? These were questions that would have to wait until Bob
and Teeka found their way back home to warn the others, with Galdov's Dark Blobs
close on their tail...

[END]
